		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>A cacophony bard is a master of manipulating sound, particularly to create dangerous waves of sound. Each cacophony learns to wield sound like a weapon, whether through artful performance or screaming and banging pots and pans together.</em></p><table><caption><p>The Cacophony</p></caption><thead><tr><th scope=\"col\"><p>Level</p></th><th scope=\"col\"><p>Features</p></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><p>3</p></td><td><p>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.MfhfSzLQbJqLCZ6q]{Blasting Volume}, @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.6LOokk0LT0GFxkpX]{One with the Noise}</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>6</p></td><td><p>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.JtnF3Tt03KgYNet5]{Echolocation}</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>10</p></td><td><p>Improved Blasting Volume</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>14</p></td><td><p>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.tbp01VZAsPYF1ZDp]{Drown Out the Voices}</p></td></tr></tbody></table><table><caption><p>Expanded Spell List</p></caption><thead><tr><th scope=\"col\"><p>Bard Level</p></th><th scope=\"col\"><p>Extra Spells</p></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><p>1</p></td><td><p><em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.NKvSCOg8Wivgexw6]{Thunderwave}</em></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>3</p></td><td><p><em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.BVd4kOcKeN5hvGk2]{Silence}</em></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>5</p></td><td><p><em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.fxREu947Lj4vCrRL]{Thundering Omen}</em></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>7</p></td><td><p><em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.CaKyglOP54Fd7ibt]{Shockwave}</em></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>9</p></td><td><p><em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.kj85kLkGaxNuoGKz]{Telepathic Bond}</em></p></td></tr></tbody></table>",
